o dance is a jamican folk form dance  with the instruments acoustic guitar, banjo, hand drums and the rhumba box\n\n{{Ska}}\n{{reggae}}\n{{folk music}}\n\n[[Category:Folk music genres]]\n[[Category:Mento| ]]\n", "name_user": "1980fast", "label": "safe", "comment": "More specific link", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mento"}
