(born 26 December 1999) is an English professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Forward (association football)|forward]] for [[Fulham F.C.|Fulham]].\n\n==Career statistics==\n{{updated|29 August 2019.}}<ref>{{Soccerway|martell-taylor-crossdale/420578}}</ref>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center\"\n|+ Appearances and goals by club, season and competition\n|-\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Club\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Season\n!colspan=\"3\"|League\n!colspan=\"2\"|[[FA Cup]]\n!colspan=\"2\"|[[EFL Cup|League Cup]]\n!colspan=\"2\"|Other\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n|-\n!Division!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n|[[Fulham F.C.|Fulham]]\n|[[2019\u201320 Fulham F.C. season|2019\u201320]]<ref name=\"EB19\">{{soccerbase season|96791|2019|accessdate=29 August 2019}}</ref>\n|[[EFL Championship|Championship]]\n|0||0||0||0||1||0||0||0||1||0\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\"|Career total\n!0!!0!!0!!0!!1!!0!!0!!0!!1!!0\n|}\n;Notes\n{{Reflist|group=lower-alpha}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Fulham F.C. squad}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Taylor-Crossdale, Martell}}\n[[Category:1999 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:English footballers]]\n[[Category:People from Edmonton (London)]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n[[Category:Chelsea F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Fulham F.C. players]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|English footballer}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=November 2019}}\n{{Use British English|date=November 2019}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n|name           = Martell Taylor-Crossdale\n|image          =\n|image_size     = \n|caption        = \n|fullname       = Martell De-Angelo Taylor-Crossdale<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.efl.com/siteassets/image/201920/general-news/efl-squad-numbering-06.09.2019.pdf |title=Notification of shirt numbers: Charlton Athletic |publisher=English Football League |page=29 |accessdate=31 March 2020}}</ref>\n|birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1999|12|26|df=y}}<ref name=\"11v11\">{{cite web