uarterfinals and semifinals, if the two teams are tied on aggregate and on [[Away goals rule|away goals]], the higher seeded team advances.<ref>per Liga MX Femenil online 'reglamentos' 2019/2020 (QF and SF) - \"De existir empate en el n\u00famero de goles, la posici\u00f3n se definir\u00e1 a favor del Club que haya anotado una mayor cantidad de goles actuando como visitante.\"</ref> In the final, if the two teams are tied after both legs, the match goes to extra time and, if necessary, a [[Penalty shoot-out (association football)|penalty shoot-out]].\n\n<!--\n{{8TeamBracket-2Leg \n| RD1=[[#Quarter-finals|Quarter-finals]]\n| RD2=[[#Semi-finals|Semi-finals]]\n| RD3=[[#Final|Final]]\n| group1=\n| group2=\n| group3=\n\n| seed-width=\n| team-width=\n| game-score-width=\n| agg-score-width=\n\n| RD1-seed01=1\n| RD1-team01=\n| RD1-score01-1=\n| RD1-score01-2=\n| RD1-score01-agg=\n| RD1-seed02=2\n| RD1-team02=\n| RD1-score02-1=\n| RD1-score02-2=\n| RD1-score02-agg=\n| RD1-seed03=3\n| RD1-team03=\n| RD1-score03-1=\n| RD1-score03-2=\n| RD1-score03-agg=\n| RD1-seed04=4\n| RD1-team04=\n| RD1-score04-1=\n| RD1-score04-2=\n| RD1-score04-agg=\n| RD1-seed05=5\n| RD1-team05=\n| RD1-score05-1=\n| RD1-score05-2=\n| RD1-score05-agg=\n| RD1-seed06=6\n| RD1-team06=\n| RD1-score06-1=\n| RD1-score06-2=\n| RD1-score06-agg=\n| RD1-seed07=7\n| RD1-team07=\n| RD1-score07-1=\n| RD1-score07-2=\n| RD1-score07-agg=\n| RD1-seed08=8\n| RD1-team08=\n| RD1-score08-1=\n| RD1-score08-2=\n| RD1-score08-agg=\n| RD2-seed01=\n| RD2-team01=\n| RD2-score01-1=\n| RD2-score01-2=\n| RD2-score01-agg=\n| RD2-seed02=\n| RD2-team02=\n| RD2-score02-1=\n| RD2-score02-2=\n| RD2-score02-agg=\n| RD2-seed03=\n| RD2-team03=\n| RD2-score03-1=\n| RD2-score03-2=\n| RD2-score03-agg=\n| RD2-seed04=\n| RD2-team04=\n| RD2-score04-1=\n| RD2-score04-2=\n| RD2-score04-agg=\n| RD3-seed01=\n| RD3-team01=\n| RD3-score01-1=\n| RD3-score01-2=\n| RD3-score01-agg=\n| RD3-seed02=\n| RD3-team02=\n| RD3-score02-1=\n| RD3-score02-2=\n| RD3-score02-agg=\n}}\n\n====Quarter-finals====\nThe first legs will be played on 27 and 28 April, and the second legs will be played on 4 and 5 May 2019.\n{{TwoLegStart}}\n{{TwoLegResult|||\u2013|||\u2013|\u2013}}\n{{TwoLegResult|||\u2013|||\u2013|\u2013}}\n{{TwoLegResult|||\u2013|||\u2013|\u2013}}\n{{TwoLegResult|||\u2013|||\u2013|\u2013}}\n{{end}}\n\n=====First leg=====\n{{Football box collapsible\n|date\t\t= \n|time\t\t= \n|team1\t\t= \n|score\t\t= \n|report\t\t= \n|team2\t\t= \n|goals1\t\t= \n|goals2\t\t=\n|location\t= \n|stadium\t= \n|attendance\t= \n|referee\t= \n}}\n{{Football box collapsible\n|date\t\t= \n|time\t\t= \n|team1\t\t= \n|score\t\t= \n|report\t\t= \n|team2\t\t= \n|goals1\t\t= \n|goals2\t\t=\n|location\t= \n|stadium\t= \n|attendance\t= \n|referee\t= \n}}\n{{Football box collapsible\n|date\t\t= \n|time\t\t= \n|team1\t\t= \n|score\t\t= \n|report\t\t= \n|team2\t\t= \n|goals1\t\t= \n|goals2\t\t=\n|location\t= \n|stadium\t= \n|attendance\t= \n|referee\t= \n}}\n{{Football box collapsible\n|date\t\t= \n|time\t\t= \n|team1\t\t= \n|score\t\t= \n|report\t\t= \n|team2\t\t= \n|goals1\t\t= \n|goals2\t\t=\n|location\t= \n|stadium\t= \n|attendance\t= \n|referee\t= \n}}\n\n=====Second leg=====\n{{Football box collapsible\n|date\t\t= \n|time\t\t= \n|team1\t\t= \n|score\t\t= \n|aggregatescore\t= \n|report\t\t= \n|team2\t\t= \n|goals1\t\t= \n|goals2\t\t= \n|location\t= \n|stadium\t= \n|attendance\t= \n|referee\t= \n}}\n{{Football box collapsible\n|date\t\t= \n|time\t\t= \n|team1\t\t= \n|score\t\t= \n|aggregatescore\t= \n|report\t\t= \n|team2\t\t= \n|goals1\t\t= \n|goals2\t\t= \n|location\t= \n|stadium\t= \n|attendance\t= \n|referee\t= \n}}\n{{Football box collapsible\n|date\t\t= \n|time\t\t= \n|team1\t\t= \n|score\t\t= \n|aggregatescore\t= \n|report\t\t= \n|team2\t\t= \n|goals1\t\t= \n|goals2\t\t= \n|location\t= \n|stadium\t= \n|attendance\t= \n|referee\t= \n}}\n{{Football box collapsible\n|date\t\t= \n|time\t\t= \n|team1\t\t= \n|score\t\t= \n|aggregatescore\t= \n|report\t\t